FBIS3-10974 "drlat051_a_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-051 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Castro Congratulates Nation's Reporters FL1503185894 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1800 GMT 15 Mar 94 FL1503185894 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Commander in Chief Fidel Castro sent a congratulatory message to all reporters of Cuba on the occasion of Cuban Media Day, which was instituted two years ago on the 100th anniversary of Jose Marti's founding of PATRIA newspaper. The message was read by Jose Ramon Balaguer during the closing of the Union of Cuban Journalists plenum. [passage omitted]
